        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: PTPRO was enriched in postsynaptic density fractions.\nPTPRO colocalized with PSD-95, confirming the postsynaptic localization.\n\n26/01/2018 Pim\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Materials and Methods\nNeuronal culture and artificial synapse formation\nCultured neurons were obtained from C57BL/6J mouse hippocampal cells" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" ;
